description.0: Deep in the swamplands of the planet Mimban lies a powerful crystal, capable of giving its possessor an invincible mastery of the Force. In the right hands, it could save the galaxy. But in the wrong hands, it could destroy it. While the explosion of the first Death Star still reverberates through the cosmos, Luke Skywalker finds that the war he thought he won was only a battle, and that the dark side of the Force still stalks the galaxy.
description.1: When an'Imperial'assassin puts'Leia'in his cross-hairs,'Chewbaccacrosses'the galaxy'to take Leia to a place of safety. But there are things in the galaxy that are worse than being assassinated, and "safety" is only relative.
description.3: Even Doctor Strange wonders what his purpose is sometimes…
description.4: Logan and his fellow X-Men go camping! Stories are swapped ‘round the campfire, and Wolverine reflects on past heartache. Cyber finds himself at the wrong end of a feeding frenzy!
description.8: Kun and Ulic Qel-Droma have a new plan to end the Republic and it involves an ancient Sith ship!
description.9: He is the one man who delivered'Han Solo'to both'Darth Vader'and'Jabbathe'Hutt. Across'the galaxy, the most-wanted criminals shudder at the mere mention of his name...'Boba Fett!
description.11: While Ben Reilly is on the search for reporter Ken Ellis, he comes face to face with an all-new menace known only as JoyStick! How will the Scarlet Spider fare in the Great Game? And how does the Green Goblin tie into everything that's going on?
description.12: Phil Urich, aka the Green Goblin, is after the new supervillain Joystick, and Joystick is after the Scarlet Spider! And the action boils over into a four-way free-for-fall when El Toro Negro enters the fray. Forget winning - can Green Goblin even survive?
description.13: Speedball faces off with a truly unique villain team--the Speedball Revenge Squad! How can Robbie beat a whole team of baddies specifically planning to take him down? Meanwhile, Scarlet Spider struggles with revealing his identity and becoming a true New Warrior...
description.14: The adventures of New York's all-new webslinger continue! The Daily Bugle is under siege, and the Scarlet Spider swings into action to save it from...the Scarlet Spider!?
description.15: Ben Reilly's life seems to be falling apart before his very eyes! With a destroyed apartment, no job and his friend still in a coma, can Ben manage to cope with all this turmoil - while steering clear of the NYPD?
description.16: Ben Reilly gets swept up in CYBERWAR! Scientist Seaward Trainer infiltrates Doctor Octopus' systems and gets access to the villain's secret plans. Will this be the edge Scarlet Spider needs to finally put an end to Ock's crime spree?
description.17: The climax of the iconic Clone Saga begins here! With the emergence of Ben Reilly as Spider-Man, where does that leave Peter Parker? Is he at last free to live a normal life?
description.19: Colossus loses his cool when he sees Kitty with her new boyfriend, Pete Wisdom!
description.20: Hulk and Betty's escape into a quiet country life has been shattered! The military has discovered their location and has taken Betty captive! Can Hulk save her without succumbing to the rage within?
description.21: Once Hawkeye's name is cleared in the case of the Avengers Mansion murder victims, it seems that Tony Stark is the killer.
description.23: Things heat up between Thor and Amora, while Curzon and Thor both realize the cause behind Yggdrasil's actions.
description.24: John Jameson recruits Spidey for a special NASA mission! Can the wall-crawler still spin a web in space?
description.26: STRANGE DAYS PART 2 Mr. Fantastic returns, alive and somewhat well! Reed Richards has been rescued the prison of time, and he's a very changed man. In addition to needing a shave, Reed finds that the FF has changed in significant ways. A joyous reunion amongst the Fantastic Four family.
description.27: A man with strange magnetic powers arrives at an orphanage late at night. He has no memory of who he is, but he bears an uncanny resemblance to the mutant villain called Magneto...
description.28: Gog and MaGog are on the hunt for the X-Babies. In order for the X-Babies to survive, Dazzler must come to their rescue.
description.30: THE FACE OF THE ENEMY REVEALED! The Starjammers reunite and escape enemy ships just in time to discover the truth about the Uncreated...
description.34: The Fantastic Four get a Skrull make-over! When the FF breeze through a small American town in their Fantasticar, all heads turn in suspicion. It's up to the Kill Krew to ensure the completion of their mission: eliminate the Skrulls at all costs!
description.35: It all collides here! It's a drag-down, knock-out brawl in Pleasant Valley, undercover suburbia of the Skrulls! Writers Mark Millar and Grant Morrison deliver an oddball conclusion to the Kill Krew saga, complete with blood, sweat, and blaster guns!
description.37: Time is running out on Hank Pym's quest to find more heroes for the final desperate battle vs. Kang, Ultron-59, Oddball, and the Grim Reaper. Only Tommy, the son of the Vision and the Scarlet Witch, elects to join Hank's cause. Sadly, the Vision, still distraught over the tragic death of his wife years ago chooses to ignore Hank's plea. So the Avengers' last roster for battle is set: Cannonball, Bombshell, Hotshot, Jessie Wingfoot, Tommy, Hank, the Wasp, and the Human Torch. When the cataclysmic confrontation kicks off in Greenwich Village, Kang and Ultron-59 quickly gain the upper hand. Cannonball, Jessie, and Hotshot are among the first heroes to fall mortally wounded. And with just the aging heroes and Tommy left standing, hope and optimism give way to gloom and despair. But many times in their glorious history, the Avengers have come back from the brink! And when Hawkeye, Mockingbird, and the Vision enter the fray, momentum begins to shift! Can Earth's Mightiest Heroes turn back the clock and snatch victory from the jaws of defeat? Avengers Assemble!
description.45: Overpowered in a war of the future, Kang makes a desperate bid to return to the present. Wasp is left bloodied and beaten following a battle with an imposter Iron Man. Giant-Man makes every attempt to save her life, but will his efforts be enough?
description.49: In order to save their friend'Smiley,'Artoo-Detoo'and'See-Threepio'have fallen in with a crew of'Targonnian'revoltists looking to overthrow'Dictator-Forever Craw. Smiley is trapped in Craw's castle, behind the palace's impenetrable'force field. To save their friend, Artoo-Detoo and See-Threepio must infiltrate the castle and shut down its protective field! The'droids'need to save Smiley because his brain contains the secret of the savorium herb, a secret which could shake'the galaxy'to its foundations!
description.50: Death stalks'Emperor'Palpatine! The Emperor's aging process is rapidly accelerating and his doom is foretold by the oracle stone. The key to his problem, the solution to his aging, is close at hand;'Han'and'Leia's youngest child,'Anakin, can reverse the process. Palpatine must kidnap young Anakin and claim the boy's body as his own! But for the sake of their son, and for the sake of'the galaxy, Han and Leia cannot let that happen, even if it means losing their own lives.
description.53: Doctor Strange ahead of his time! Watch him pitch some investors on a Virtual Reality headset, before he's suddenly transported to the Magic Dimension. Awkward timing I'm sure.
description.56: Five years after the'Empire's defeat in'Return of the Jedi, the forces of the Empire have rallied. Even as'Luke Skywalker'searches for'Jedi'to join him in the inevitable battle,'Grand Admiral'Thrawn, the last of the'Emperor's warlords, schemes with'Joruus C'baoth'to end the battle before it can begin. Out-manned, out-numbered, and sorely out-gunned, Luke fears there is no hope. It's up to him to challenge Thrawn, the heir to the Empire.
description.57: Those responsible for the Coruscant attack stand trial.  But has their quest for dominance only just begun?
description.58: Look out, Peter – there’s a new webslinger in town! Ben Reilly, AKA The Scarlet Spider! But he’s not the only new kid on the block – there’s a new Doctor Octopus too, and she’s trapped Ben in a virtual reality nightmare? Can he make it out alive – or is the Scarlet Spider’s saga over before it even begins?
description.59: The New Warriors take on the Soldiers of Misfortune beneath the ocean to stop a drug cartel!
description.60: The legendary Clone Saga continues with the all-new wall-crawler...the Scarlet Spider! Ben Reilly's boss Jason Tso has been made a target. His pursuer - a mysterious mercenary known only as the Pro!
description.61: While searching for answers, Ben Reilly gets caught up in a confrontation with the artificial Animen!
description.62: VIRTUAL MORTALITY reaches its inevitable climax! Ben at last discovers the endgame to Doctor Octopus' intricate plan.
description.63: Ben Reilly is revealed as Spider-Man! But what will this shocking twist mean for the life of Peter Parker?
description.64: VIRTUAL MORTALITY begins here! It's a day in the life for Ben Reilly, as his new job as a nightclub waiter is going great - until he spots the new Doctor Octopus up to no good!
description.65: Iron Man orders lockdown on Avengers Mansion to prevent any tampering of evidence. Space phantoms Malachi and Tobias, along with an imposter Luna, set a deviant plan into action. Will the Swordsman and Vision be able to stop the trio from capturing the Cotati?
description.70: Excalibur unwinds at a local pub where Kitty and Pete reveal they're taking their relationship to the next level!
description.71: The Incredible Hulk vs. the Rampaging Rhino...in baseball? How in the world did this wacky sitaution come to pass?
description.72: As Tony's blackouts worsen, evidence continues to mount, implicating Stark as the killer of the victims from Avengers Mansion.
description.74: With strange things happening in New York, Detective Curzon and Code: Blue have reason to suspect its connected to a "dying ash tree". Back in Asgard, Odin expects an unwanted guest.
description.75: When Sandman escapes police custody, he returns to his old wicked ways of robbing banks and committing crime! Can Spider-Man reach a deal with this deadly foe?
description.77: STRANGE DAYS PART 1 Meet Hyperstorm, the future child of Franklin Richards and Rachel Summers! Ant-Man discovers who the Tomorrow Man really is, and the answer will shock you! Doom returns, but not in the way you're expecting.
description.78: As the threat of the Legacy Virus looms over mutantkind, Professor Xavier and Beast attempt to downplay its severity...
description.79: Cyber is presented to Genesis, and the results are diabolical. Vindicator and Guardian must save Wolverine from himself when he flies off the handle battling Dirtnap. Do Heather and James Hudson really have cause for concern?
description.80: Gambit and Bishop save the X-Babies from a unruly mob.
description.83: An Alternaverse tale revealing the final fate of the Avengers! When Ultron slaughters the futures heroes, an elderly Hank Pym must assemble all the crimefighters he can to re-earn the name Avengers! But can the daughter of She-Hulk, a blind Hawkeye, an aged Human Torch and the mutant called Cannonball defeat the villains that killed the Earth's Mightiest Heroes?
description.86: A new villain arrives on the scene for the Starjammers to battle...they call him The "Uncreated"!
description.87: The team gives Boomer an intervention about her constant visits to Sabretooth and how it could put herself and everyone in danger. Will the wise words finally change her mind? Or will it just add fuel to the fire in her strange addiction?
description.90: The Krew explores the outer limits of their shapeshifting abilities against the many heads of Hydra! Why is Baron Von Strucker getting involved in Skrull business? The answer will surprise you! Guest-starring Captain America.
description.97: After a failed attempt to rescue the hapless'Smiley'from the clutches of Dictator-Forever Craw,'Artoo'and'Threepio'find themselves captives in Craw's palace! And, as if life weren't already complicated enough for Threepio and Artoo, a revolution breaks out inside the palace grounds! They came to save their friend, but now they're fighting to save themselves!
description.98: The'Emperor'is back, and this time he's out for blood! Following his battle with'Luke Skywalker'in'Dark Empire II, Emperor Palpatine was forced to occupy an inferior'clone-body. That body is now aging rapidly, and Palpatine's final, irrevocable end is near unless he can infuse his line of clones with genetic material from a'Jedi'bloodline. His target:'Han'and Leia's youngest child,'Anakin!
description.99: The war of good against evil has been waged for centuries. It began long before Ranulf joined the Imperials, long before he was ever born, and the war will continue long after he is dead. But now Ranulf is forced to fight one battle of this war, a battle that rages in his soul. When Governor Grigor's Imperial forces clash with Princess Leia's Rebels, Ranulf must choose between his Imperial allies and the Rebel he has come to love...and the outcome of his personal battle may change the current of this River of Chaos!

2.text: Psylocke, Beast, and Wolverine travel to Florida to investigate a reported sightings of the vampire called Bloodscream…

3.text: Even Doctor Strange wonders what his purpose is sometimes…

4.text: Logan and his fellow X-Men go camping! Stories are swapped ‘round the campfire, and Wolverine reflects on past heartache. Cyber finds himself at the wrong end of a feeding frenzy!

5.text: Finally returning from the future, Cable and Domino find themselves smack in then middle of an all-out war! What happened to cause such a savage conflict to flare up like this?

6.text: OPERATION REBIRTH PART 2 Cap and Sharon Carter form an uneasy alliance with Red Skull to lay siege to a supertech fortress! Will the trio be able to put aside their differences long enough to complete their mission? Find out here!

7.text: Banshee lies near death as Emma Frost tries to save him. What thoughts lurk in the minds of dying men?

18.text: Daredevil (Matt Murdock) takes on Daredevil (Sir)! A battle of the alter egos you just can’t miss!

22.text: Dana’s death by Venom tears a hole in Miguel’s relationship with Xina. What will Spider-Man uncover about the symbiote through extensive research? And, Kasey Nash, pursued by Vulture!

31.text: Holocaust and Sebastian Shaw enter a dangerous alliance…one that will have devastating consequences for the X-Force squad!

32.text: Nate is the topic of conversation when Blaquesmith confronts Professor Xavier at the X-Mansion. Can Xavier track Nate…even on the astral plane?

39.text: Wolverine and Gambit's mission is twofold: discover the secrets behind the London murders and take down Arcade and Mastermind. Answers revealed! Blood spilled! Justice served!

40.text: Venom is attracted…to Eddie Brock's ex-wife! The symbiote threatens to not only break Anne's heart…but her entire body too!

41.text: X-Force and Cable are supposed to be relaxing at an island resort. But when frequent FF foil Impossible Man makes an appearance (with his meddlesome kids in tow), this vacation getaway turns into an on-the-clock adventure!

42.text: Force Works draws the gaze of Apocryphus when they land in Vietnam to find the Temple of Agaphaur.

43.text: Deathunt 9000 leads a group of cyborg soldiers to track down Hawkeye…but War Machine comes to the rescue!

44.text: Bruce Banner must come to terms with all the nightmarish iterations of his Hulk alter egos. Featuring the Ringmaster!

46.text: Doom makes a bid for peace with Morphine Somers to gain Billy the Kid’s tech. The White House is remodeled into a post-industrial house of horrors.

47.text: Relive Peter Parker's first days as an amazing wall-crawler with this fully-painted special!

48.text: The Inner Circle is a group of powerful elites who have set their sights on none other than Jean Grey!

51.text: Generation X vs. a fire-breathing dragon!

53.text: Doctor Strange ahead of his time! Watch him pitch some investors on a Virtual Reality headset, before he's suddenly transported to the Magic Dimension. Awkward timing I'm sure.

54.text: Cable and Domino head back to the future! It's a race against time as the two battle-hardened mutants fight to save the life of…Nathan Summers!?

55.text: OPERATION REBIRTH PART 1 Captain America emerges from an icy prison to find himself in a mysterious facility. With the outside world convinced that the Sentinel of Liberty is dead, Cap must find a way to return to the world he is sworn to protect!

But he’s not the only new kid on the block – there’s a new Doctor Octopus too, and she’s trapped Ben in a virtual reality nightmare? Can he make it out alive – or is the Scarlet Spider’s saga over before it even begins?

66.text: Doom 2099 slips in his control to undo John Herod’s masterstroke. Punisher 2099, Jake Gallows, becomes a wanted fugitive, while the X-Men of 2099 band together in their own city-state.

67.text: Storm is out of control and wrecking havoc in the Savage Land!

68.text: While Cannonball saves Husk, his sister, X-Men and Storm battle a battalion of Nimrods.

69.text: Who’s the Daredevil in the red and yellow suit?!

73.text: Xina and Dana are captives of Venom 2099! Plus, flashback to see how Miguel and Dana first got together…right under the noses of his brother Gabriel and his then-girlfriend Xina!

85.text: Mastermind has flung Gambit and Wolverine into a twisted version of their own memories. When things start to get hectic, a disoriented Wolverine lashes out at Gambit. Will these former teammates survive Mastermind's trap?

87.text: The team gives Boomer an intervention about her constant visits to Sabretooth and how it could put herself and everyone in danger. Will the wise words finally change her mind? Or will it just add fuel to the fire in her strange addiction?

88.text: Nate and the Dark Beast come to blows…and Blaquesmith lurks on the horizon.

91.text: Peter Parker and Miguel O'Hara are thrust into each other’s time streams! How will Spidey 2099 fare in modern day New York? Peter faces Vulture 2099 in Nueva York…while Miguel takes on Eddie Brock’s Venom!

92.text: Eddie finds a miracle cure to save his ex-wife from her symbiotic madness!

93.text: Amid the team's induction of Cybermancer as their newest member, Iron Man shares some distressing news about the death of Marilla.

94.text: Phil approaches the New Warriors to become their newest hero addition -- but forgets that he's dressed up as a villain!

95.text: War Machine takes on a new investigation when a bodybuilder develops Hulk-like strength after consuming steroids.

96.text: A terrifying, anthropomorphic man-spider is causing mayhem at Syntha East’s Bio-Development Lab. What strange science is behind this monstrosity, and can Miguel find the underlying cause of it before another victim falls?
